Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: django-json-trans
Version: 0.1
Summary: A Django app that provides model field translations with JSON Fields.
Home-page: https://github.com/Mostaard/django-json-trans
Author: Jonas Vandermosten
Author-email: Jonfffffas@mostaard.be
License: BSD-3-Clause
Description: ========================
        Django JSON Translations
        ========================
        
        Django JSON Translations is an app that provides a field for storing
        translations in PostgreSQL JSON fields.
        
        Config
        -----------
        
        Add the supported languages in settings as following
        LANGUAGES = [
        ('en', _('English')),
        ('nl', _('Dutch')),
        ('fr', _('French')),
        ]
        
